'''白沙罗市中心站'''（{{lang-ms|Stesen MRT Pusat Bandar Damansara}}）位於[[吉隆坡|吉隆坡]][[白沙罗_(吉隆坡)|白沙罗]][[西部疏散大道|西部疏散大道]]的马洛夫路交通枢纽之上（出口2315D），是[[巴生谷捷运|巴生谷]][[加影线|加影线]]的其中一个[[高架车站|高架]][[捷运|捷运]]车站，主要服务[[白沙罗市中心|白沙罗市中心]]、[[白沙罗高原|白沙罗高原]]及[[孟沙|孟沙]]等[[白沙罗_(吉隆坡)|白沙罗]]一带的居民。本站属于双加捷运第一阶段线路，于2016年12月16日开始运营。<ref name=MRT>{{cite news|title=首相正式启动第一阶段双加线|url=http://www.mymrt.com.my/cms/upload_files/mediarelease/mediarelease_download_000923.pdf|accessdate=2016-12-19|publisher=Mass Rapid Transit Corporation Sdn Bhd|date=2016-12-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305001836/http://www.mymrt.com.my/cms/upload_files/mediarelease/mediarelease_download_000923.pdf|archivedate=2017-03-05}}</ref><ref name=Malay16122016>{{cite news|last1=Ruban|first1=A.|title=A quiet start to Malaysia’s first MRT, but commuters happy|url=http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/a-quiet-start-to-malaysias-first-mrt-but-commuters-happy|accessdate=2016-12-18|work=The Malay Mail Online|date=2016-12-16|archive-date=2017-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804101820/http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/a-quiet-start-to-malaysias-first-mrt-but-commuters-happy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=捷运双加线首阶段通车．双溪毛糯至士曼丹免费乘搭1个月|url=http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1596685/捷运双加线首阶段通车．双溪毛糯至士曼丹免费乘搭1个月|accessdate=2017-07-22|publisher=[[星洲网|星洲网]]|date=2017-12-16|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511101145/http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1596685/%E6%8D%B7%E8%BF%90%E5%8F%8C%E5%8A%A0%E7%BA%BF%E9%A6%96%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E9%80%9A%E8%BD%A6%EF%BC%8E%E5%8F%8C%E6%BA%AA%E6%AF%9B%E7%B3%AF%E8%87%B3%E5%A3%AB%E6%9B%BC%E4%B8%B9%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E4%B9%98%E6%90%AD1%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 车站结构 ==
此站设计类似其他标准架空车站，一共有两个楼层和地面层，设有两个出口，分别位于道路的两侧。

白沙罗市中心站還會在站名前加入「柏威年白沙罗高原广场」（Pavilion Damansara Heights）商标，以作為命名權計劃的一部分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marketing-interactive.com/mrt-corp-rebrands-four-stations-as-part-of-station-naming-rights-programme/|title=MRT Corp rebrands 4 stations as part of station naming rights programme|publisher=Marketing Interactive|date=2017-07-12|accessdate=2017-07-19|archive-date=2020-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327210105/https://www.marketing-interactive.com/mrt-corp-rebrands-four-stations-as-part-of-station-naming-rights-programme|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theedgemarkets.com/article/jendela-mayang-kuala-lumpur-pavilion-among-those-awarded-naming-rights-mrt-stations|title=Jendela Mayang, Kuala Lumpur Pavilion among those awarded naming rights to MRT stations|publisher=The Edge Markets|date=2017-07-11|accessdate=2017-07-19|archive-date=2020-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327210108/https://www.theedgemarkets.com/article/jendela-mayang-kuala-lumpur-pavilion-among-those-awarded-naming-rights-mrt-stations|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==接驳巴士==
加影线车站皆提供接驳巴士服务。本站提供前往[[白沙罗高原|白沙罗高原]]和金地花园若干住宅区和[[谷中城|谷中城]]的服务。本站也提供接驳至[[吉隆坡中央车站|吉隆坡中央车站]]的服务，是吉隆坡城市铁路网唯一拥有此项服务的车站。接驳巴士将停留于入口B的巴士站。<ref>{{cite news|title=捷运接驳巴士路线|url=http://www.spad.gov.my/land-public-transport/buses/mrt-feeder-bus-routes|accessdate=2017-07-20|publisher=[[陆路公共交通委员会|陆路公共交通委员会]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170723130349/http://www.spad.gov.my/land-public-transport/buses/mrt-feeder-bus-routes|archive-date=2017-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=MRT Pusat Bandar Damansara (T817) & (T818) - Door B|url=http://www.spad.gov.my/sites/default/files/mrt_pusat_bandar_damansara_t817_t818_pintu_b.pdf|work=[[陆路公共交通委员会|陆路公共交通委员会]]|language=ms|format=PDF|access-date=2017-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809033409/http://www.spad.gov.my/sites/default/files/mrt_pusat_bandar_damansara_t817_t818_pintu_b.pdf|archive-date=2017-08-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=MRT Pusat Bandar Damansara (T819) & (T820) - Door B|url=http://www.spad.gov.my/sites/default/files/mrt_pusat_bandar_damansara_t819_t820_pintu_b.pdf|work=[[陆路公共交通委员会|陆路公共交通委员会]]|language=ms|format=PDF|access-date=2017-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822113309/http://www.spad.gov.my/sites/default/files/mrt_pusat_bandar_damansara_t819_t820_pintu_b.pdf|archive-date=2017-08-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

